Crack the Clue II was a community event released on 22nd February, 2019.
The Mimic and beginner clues were released as a part of the Treasure Trail expansion on 11th April, 2019.
House Hosidius in Kourend was reworked graphically on 23rd May, 2019.
The Forthos dungeon was released on 4th July, 2019.
The Last Man Standing minigame was reworked and released on 29th August, 2019.
The Fremennik Exiles is a master level quest that was released on 26th September, 2019.
The Twisted League was the first league and was released on 14th November, 2019.
The Nightmare of Ashihama was released on 6th February, 2020.
The Song of the Elves is a grandmaster quest which unlocked access to Prifddinas on 25th July, 2019.
The Death system rework was released on 24th June, 2020.
The Mahogany Homes update to construction was released on 26th August, 2020.
The Ferox Enclave PvP outpost in the wilderness was released on 16th July, 2020.
The Porcine of Interest is a novice level quest which was released on 10th September, 2020.
The Soul Wars minigame was the first in a series of backported pieces of content and was released on 6th January, 2021.
Sins of the Father is a Master quest which unlocked access to Darkmeyer on 4th June, 2020.
The Shades of Mort'ton rework was released on 27th January, 2021.
The Trailblazer League was the second league and was released on 28th October, 2020.
Tzhaar-Ket-Rak's challenges which introduced the ability to fight 6 jads at once was released on 3rd March, 2021.
Shooting Stars is a distraction and diversion mining activity which was released on 17th March, 2021.
Tempoross the fishing skill boss was released on 24th March, 2021.
Below Ice Mountain is a free-to-play quest which was released on 14th April, 2021.
The Combat Achievements system was released on 21st July, 2021.
A Kingdom Divided is a master level quest which was released on 16th June, 2021.
Deadman: Reborn was a seasonal event released on 25th August, 2021.
The Group Ironman gamemode was released on 6th October, 2021.
Nex: The Fifth General was released and added to the Godwars Dungeon on 5th January, 2022.
The Shattered Relics League was the third league and was released on 19th January, 2022.
Land of the Goblins is an experienced level quest and was released on 9th February, 2022.
Phosani's Nightmare was released on 30th June, 2021.
The Revenant Maledictus boss was released and added to the revenant caves on 2nd February, 2022.
The Temple of the Eye quest which unlocked access to the Guardians of the Rift minigame was released on 23rd March, 2022.
The Giants' Foundry minigame was released on 8th June, 2022.
The Emir's Arena is a ranked pvp minigame which was released on 13th July, 2022.
The Unranked Group Ironman gamemode was released on 26th May, 2022.
The Secrets of the North is a master level quest which introduced the Phantom Muspah boss and was released on 11th January, 2023.
Quest Speedrunning is a minigame which was released on 12th October, 2022.
The Venenatis, Callisto and Vet'ion bosses were reworked on 25th January, 2023.
Raids III: Tombs of Amascut was released on 24th August, 2022.
